snippet.title: Lemmings: Atari Lynx (1993)
snippet.description:
Intro and gameplay from Lemmings on the Atari Lynx, released in 1993.
Developed by DMA Design Limited and published by Psygnosis

Game credits:
- Brian Johnston - Music
- Brian Watson - Code
- Jamie Grant - Graphics
- Mike Dailly - Graphics
- Scott Johnston - Graphics
- Steve Hammond - Code (Level editor)
- Tim Wright - Music
- Tony Williams - Music

Watch other editions of the Lemmings game here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW_a1Ic-Y4n_sYe2n1OCwe0j03EOxxq3U

Enjoy the video? Remember to like, comment and subscribe to Retro Gaming TV - http://bit.ly/2N5gjMA
